{
  "stem": "935.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I didn't get to see her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had looked in the-- little-- in the children's lockers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the nuns' rooms, there was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came back the next morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The whole orphanage had changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were clothes hanging outside, winter clothes, all colors, lots of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a whole bunch of children were there, different children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What had happened, there was one Nazi who had decided that the Schouwburg, this theater, was not good for children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Even though they were being sent on transport a day or two later with their parents, this was no place for children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they sent them to the orphanage-- which was not at all prepared, for we had no-- no-- nothing there-- to be taken care of them for a day or two or three until they go with their parents on transport.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there one night, I had the night shift.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had bombed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Even though there was no bombing in Amsterdam then, our building was on fire, and I was with the children in the basement.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I met there three Dutch guys from the underground who had come to meet me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They knew all about me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I knew nothing about them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The purpose was to help them save some of the children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The idea was to get me back on the day shift.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then we had permission-- Mother Superior had gotten permission to go with the children for a walk, weather permitting, around blocks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Always the same four blocks, three times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And at that time, on one-- the last block, there was a little house set way back from the street, like a little cloister.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And one of the guys would be waiting there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
